-- Norwich Signs Celtic Striker Gary Hooper to Three-Year Contract
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-07-26T13:47:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-26/norwich-signs-celtic-striker-gary-hooper-to-three-year-contract.html
Norwich City signed Celtic striker
 Gary Hooper  to a three-year contract, the Premier League soccer
club said on its website.  Terms of the agreement, which includes a club option for a
fourth season, weren’t disclosed.  Hooper, 25, was Celtic’s top scorer in each of his three
seasons with the club, recording 82 goals in 137 games. He
helped Celtic win two Scottish Premier League titles and two
Scottish F.A. Cups and was twice named to the SPL team of the
year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  